[i]Warping Flames[/i] – Whenever a source you control deals noncombat damage to a creature, you may exile that creature. If you do, its controller may cast it from exile for as long as it remains exiled.
[i]Crit[/i] – Whenever Sonya deals combat damage to a player, Sonya deals X damage to that player, where X is the number of artifacts that player controls.
[i]Promoted Class[/i] – {1}{B}{R}
